snippet.title: Mario Royale Deluxe (now Legacy, more in description) - Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's a trailer for Mario Royale Deluxe.

For clarification, Mario Royale Deluxe was officially made public on February 11th, 2023.
It's no longer available, Mario Royale "Legacy" is back instead with many improvements and additions since Mario Royale's original release. Check it out, still at https://marioroyale.com

Music used: "Versus Overworld" NSMB Remix
by NoteBlock (thanks)

MARIO AND ALL RELATED ASSETS ARE PROPERTY OF NINTENDO CO. LTD.

MARIO ROYALE DELUXE IS A REMASTER OF INFERNOPLUS' ORIGINAL MARIO ROYALE CREATED IN 2019

ALL GAME ASSETS ARE PROPERTIES OF THEIR RESPECTIVE OWNERS.
